---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="content">
			<h1>Data Deletion Request</h1>
			<p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 1.1.2025</p>

			<h2>How to Delete Your Data</h2>
			<p>If you wish to delete your personal data that we hold, please follow these steps:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Email Us:</strong> Send an email to <a href="mailto:benjamin@meixner.org">benjamin@meixner.org</a>.</li>
				<li><strong>Subject Line:</strong> Use "Data Deletion Request" as the subject.</li>
				<li><strong>Include Details:</strong> Provide your name and any identifying information related to your account (specifically your phone number used for WhatsApp).</li>
				<li><strong>Verification:</strong> We may need to verify your identity before processing the deletion.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Processing Time</h2>
			<p>We aim to process all deletion requests within 30 days. You will receive a confirmation once your data has been deleted.</p>

			<h2>Contact Us</h2>
			<p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact us at <a href="mailto:benjamin@meixner.org">benjamin@meixner.org</a>.</p>

			<a href="/" class="back-link">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.content {
		padding: 4rem 0;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	h1 {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		color: var(--secondary);
	}

	h2 {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--primary-dark);
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}

	p, ul {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--text);
	}

	ul {
		padding-left: 2rem;
	}

	li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	a {
		color: var(--primary);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.back-link {
		display: inline-block;
		margin-top: 2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
	}
</style>